Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話和一般人沒什麼兩樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此也不能隨便使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.50,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事情都要支付代價 我教過你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的力量不是為了個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是為了眾生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長老
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 遲到了真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊布拉的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.10,staff@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H118FD0&\fs54\move(270,280,210,280,1,150)\3a&H80&}代號 「長老」{\clip(0,0,209,720)}
